Hosting the 1961 Local Government Elections datasets and associated metadata files
**NOTICE OF UPDATE (29/12/2025)
- Revisions to different 1961 Local Government files to accommodate corrections, addition of independent symbols and revisions to the metadata and other source files
**NOTICE OF CORRECTION (14/1/2026)
- Spelling correction for one of Trengganu wards
**NOTICE OF UPDATE (1/4/2026)
- Added a file showing Vote and Seat Distribution for every local government for the 1961 Elections. This is based on Tindak Malaysia's interpretation. One should read the metadata for the 1961 elections to understand discrepancies underpinning the dataset
- Added a file showing Vote and Seat Distribution at the state level for the 1961 Election. This data comes strictly from the Election Commission's 1961 report and Tindak Malaysia doesn't vouch for complete accuracy of the presented data by the Election Commission report
